PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of Quebec which provides for the making of a financial contribution to the Quebec Farm Income Stabilization Insurance Program for the years 1991, 1992 and 1993, in order to protect the income of grain, oilseed and potato producers.
